    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! Thanks for taking a look at my pride and joy. Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to even think about parting with this beauty. I\u2019ve treated her like royalty since day one\u2014always tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and only ever hand-washed with the good stuff. The paint still has that deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is so crisp you'd swear it just rolled off the assembly line. It drives like an absolute dream, smooth and responsive, just like the day I first picked it up. You might find a microscopic pebble chip if you really go hunting, but in my eyes, she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come. If you're looking for a car that\u2019s been truly pampered and is ready for a new home, I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
